(42143, 'ptBR', 'O chamado dos campeões [WIP]', '[PH] Interact with the Mission Table and complete \"The Dalaran Situation.\"', '[PH] Greetings, $c. Beside me is the Mission Table. From it, you can assign our troops to complete vital assignments across the Broken Isles.$B$BGive it a try now, master. We have received word of a small demon attack on the city of Dalaran. Let us send someone to help repel the enemy.$B$BGaze upon the Mission Table and send a Champion to Dalaran.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 38134),
